original_title: T-ARA Japan Tour 2013 - Treasure Box- 2nd TOUR FINAL In Budokan
overview: The second Japan nationwide concert tour by South Korean girl group T-ARA, in support of their second Japanese studio album, Treasure Box (2013). The tour began on September 4, 2013, at Fukuoka Sun Palace, Japan and ended on September 27 at the Nippon Budokan in Tokyo, Japan.
title: T-ARA Japan Tour 2013 - Treasure Box- 2nd TOUR FINAL In Budokan
